0.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁頂級前鋒, 利雲果D 有無7成?</blockquote><br />\n好難就咁計<br />\n你打反擊一個直線比個前鋒有兩三秒睇定黎射就點都要入<br />\n但有d你攞到個波個龍已經封到埋黎就有56成都算唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見D 講波佬講到單刀必入咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0abeb3159788e4797d15a1bd0884db7250bbe4a","tid":44773,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"無一個標準答案?"},{"pid":"8d112fd857791fe87e26aeedb9cd03cafcf5f4ba","tid":44773,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"參考下3、4年前拜超高美斯入攝單刀把握"},{"pid":"b897bb7ff60993de2b92d0c1d532581e135b61de","tid":44773,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50%<br />\n<br />\n一係入，一係唔入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完樓上成班on9認真討論<br />\n最後反而覺得第一個回覆最有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb95a6200b4978ecfd37f755c4f0a543d825a59","tid":44773,"uid":52349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T23:56:58.000Z","msg":"全盛 VV  扑單刀真係一流"},{"pid":"bb030ad7e790e6c5c6e4fe4806e6badab0048f5c","tid":44773,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>50%<br />\n<br />\n一係入，一係唔入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完樓上成班on9認真討論<br />\n最後反而覺得第一個回覆最有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\